    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. so it basically says if i make a mistake, i'm on the hook for all their legal costs too right? that seems pretty intense. are there usually hidden ways these things can bite you that aren't obvious at first glance?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
